wt.workflow.engine

Class WfDuration

  • java.lang.Object
    • wt.workflow.engine.WfDuration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, Evolvable

    public class WfDuration
extends java.lang.Object
implements Evolvable
    This class is to be used for variable modification of a process' or activity's deadline duration.. If the deadline duration is set in the workflow template's deadline tab, that value will be used, rounded to the nearest whole, day as the default to populate this variable. This variable's default value is zero days.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
